To run the game you should download this environment: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1zavWM4cbdIA3vTMZLlWtr0GXC5t0rvE1

after setup DOS application you should put these files in one directory with the game assembly file then open DOS and type this commands.

1- mount d "the drive in which the directory is" :/  (mountd d d:/).
2- d:
3- cd " the directory after the drive"
4- masm "game file name".asm
5-link "game file name".obj
6- "game file name".exe

now you can play.
